VOLUME DUE TO THE CONTINUED SLOWDOWN IN CONSTRUCTION SPENDING, AND DISCIPLINED UNDERWRITING. THE DECREASE ALSO REFLECTED THE IMPACT OF REDUCTIONS IN SURETY REINSURANCE COSTS IN 2010 ASSOCIATED WITH

