ADJUSTMENT EXPENSE RATIO IN 2011 AND 2010, RESPECTIVELY. NET FAVORABLE PRIOR YEAR RESERVE DEVELOPMENT PROVIDED 1.5 POINTS AND 1.2 POINTS OF BENEFIT TO THE LOSS AND LOSS ADJUSTMENT EXPENSE RATIO IN

