AMOUNTS OF DEBT OBLIGATIONS, OTHER THAN COMMERCIAL PAPER, THAT BECOMES DUE IN 2012 AND 2013 ARE $250 MILLION AND $500 MILLION, RESPECTIVELY. IN 2014, NO DEBT

