3. INVESTMENTS (CONTINUED)

DISTRIBUTION.

THE COMPANY'S MAXIMUM EXPOSURE TO LOSS WITH RESPECT TO THESE INVESTMENTS IS LIMITED TO THE INVESTMENT CARRYING AMOUNTS REPORTED IN THE COMPANY'S CONSOLIDATED BALANCE SHEET AND ANY

UNFUNDED COMMITMENT. NEITHER THE CARRYING AMOUNTS NOR THE UNFUNDED COMMITMENTS RELATED TO THESE VIES ARE MATERIAL.

