EXPECTED LOSS DEVELOPMENT FOR LIABILITY LINES OF BUSINESS, DRIVEN BY THE FIDUCIARY PRODUCT FOR ACCIDENT YEARS 2008 AND PRIOR. IN INTERNATIONAL, NET FAVORABLE DEVELOPMENT IN 2011 REFLECTED BETTER THAN

EXPECTED LOSS DEVELOPMENT IN CANADA, PRIMARILY IN THE SURETY, DIRECTORS AND OFFICERS, AND GENERAL LIABILITY LINES OF BUSINESS FOR RECENT ACCIDENT YEARS AND BETTER THAN EXPECTED DEVELOPMENT IN THE

