RESPECTIVELY. THE QUALIFIED DOMESTIC PLAN ACCOUNTED FOR $2.65 BILLION AND $2.37 BILLION OF THE TOTAL ACCUMULATED BENEFIT OBLIGATION AT DECEMBER 31, 2011 AND 2010, RESPECTIVELY,

